{"tid":916871,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"住悦湖個邊嘅麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2018-11-26T03:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T16:10:52.000Z","uid":220860,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"68af43288ac8fc22e755b354d2218e7488daa217","tid":916871,"uid":220860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"悅湖以前間唯美小食轉左手之後真係好撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢係咁加我都算,屌你啲小食仲要愈來愈垃圾，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴晚見有d餓,落去買左椰菜餃,雞串。見到佢煎雞之前扔左串雞落魚蛋湯個邊浸一浸,跟住求其落d油煎下就問我辣唔辣,我真係睇到呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屌你你咁撚樣我不如自己煮白烚雞柳,食落口完全唔香口,又油淋淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 椰菜餃又係求其煎下就算撚數。食落口d皮唔脆,仲要層皮仲厚過我層腳皮#haha#屌你快d執柒左佢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收錢個四眼呀哥係幾好禮貌,但可唔可以煮好啲野食呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8359108db9622fcdbaec06a6060655cc8adcbc85","tid":916871,"uid":222966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"以前真係好好食<br />\n<br />\n轉左手真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞串真係熟到食唔落"},{"pid":"409e8504d85a1de1e06b76695ed100a45575254c","tid":916871,"uid":211234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"食OK後面新開嗰檔串燒好撚過"},{"pid":"6a2c47eed8bf282a115b9a95a4e6e6dc49426c6e","tid":916871,"uid":220860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8359108db9622fcdbaec06a6060655cc8adcbc85","tid":916871,"uid":222966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"以前真係好好食<br />\n<br />\n轉左手真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞串真係熟到食唔落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"咪就係,以前雞串又香又脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class